==[[Mbabaram]]==
===Etymology===
Not a borrowing from English, but an independent and regular development from the proto-Australian word *'''gudaga''', thus: Mbabaram '''dog''' < *'''dwog(a)''' < *'''udwoga''' < *'''gudwaga''' < proto-Australian *'''gudaga'''. Cf. [[Dyirbal]] '''guda'''.

